{"tid":925764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊以「衝紅燈」反駁：嚴厲執法算不算搬龍門？","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T05:36:08.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"adbcd1136a67b4435a144f21c5f106283cb4cca2","tid":925764,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"參選鄉郊代表選舉的自決派立法會議員朱凱廸，兩度遭選舉主任查問是否提倡或支持「港獨」是自決前途的選項問題後，昨收到選舉主任的通知，直指他隱晦地確認了支持「獨立」是香港人一個選項，因此裁定其提名無效。<br />\n朱凱廸昨日質疑選舉主任決定是政治審查，認為政府在任意「搬龍門」，而行政會議成員湯家驊就以「衝紅燈」作例子，否認政府「搬龍門」之說。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊昨晚在Facebook分享一條題為「朱凱廸稱從沒主張港獨 批評政府任意『搬龍門』」的新聞，並留言：「容許我問一個愚蠢問題，假若有日甲衝紅燈，警察看不見，沒他辦法。第二天，乙見到甲衝紅燈沒事，他也衝紅燈，警察又看不見，沒檢控乙。當區警司知道了大怒，下令警察加緊巡邏，嚴厲執法，這算不算『搬龍門』？」"},{"pid":"b56ad04781d67122f43781251a852d56ff2f6c6b","tid":925764,"uid":84633,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"11哥衰11不特止?<br />\n<br />\n仲要衝紅燈?"},{"pid":"ee6d0592baf264b2042227ae42e9ff99fd329b82","tid":925764,"uid":104106,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b56ad04781d67122f43781251a852d56ff2f6c6b","tid":925764,"uid":84633,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"11哥衰11不特止?<br />\n<br />\n仲要衝紅燈?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"衝紅燈好唔衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f810b9c94916abf45969aa9fc7c344eb96f758","tid":925764,"uid":63154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"嚴厲執咗一堆越境魚船先啦你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d6ce50fd801c8aa21c1e8cee6c2a7751c86dd6","tid":925764,"uid":84633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee6d0592baf264b2042227ae42e9ff99fd329b82","tid":925764,"uid":104106,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b56ad04781d67122f43781251a852d56ff2f6c6b","tid":925764,"uid":84633,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"11哥衰11不特止?<br />\n<br />\n仲要衝紅燈?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"衝紅燈好唔衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"未成年隨時破埋人處<br />\n<br />\n都係血淋淋"},{"pid":"13d41dffc204cf888bb52bb0e7fe0e64d025d0c5","tid":925764,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d6ce50fd801c8aa21c1e8cee6c2a7751c86dd6","tid":925764,"uid":84633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee6d0592baf264b2042227ae42e9ff99fd329b82","tid":925764,"uid":104106,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b56ad04781d67122f43781251a852d56ff2f6c6b","tid":925764,"uid":84633,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"11哥衰11不特止?<br />\n<br />\n仲要衝紅燈?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"衝紅燈好唔衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"未成年隨時破埋人處<br />\n<br />\n都係血淋淋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"男仔點紅燈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a8d04bfcb476f2f40023f190540b9ca430cb95","tid":925764,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"咦<br />\n佢挑戰緊香港警察既「選擇性執法」喎<br />\n哈係咪黐撚左線"},{"pid":"8e0a0fc8d091873660bc4efe20ae5f5cd61523a7","tid":925764,"uid":81141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"又唔見嚴厲執蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea200c4b7ec5d4226c067d690f60008b25c9e2cd","tid":925764,"uid":20498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"有人衰十一可以無事...仲有得加官進爵...<br />\n有人崇尚民主自由人權會換來身敗名裂...<br />\n<br />\n咁呢個算係咩???"},{"pid":"8f5a9832d470c746e5e398eac